<para>The handle to the created client. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">mesh_query</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The pointer to intialized <ref refid="struct_m_l_occlusion_mesh_query" kindref="compound">MLOcclusionMeshQuery</ref> struct. </para>
